@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

@{MS "Introduction"}

If you're often using a CD player or video player software, then I guess you
wished to have a remote control like for your real CD player.@{par}

This is what IRComRemote does. But there is more much more. You can use your
entire computer by using a normal remote control.@{par}

You will love it. Flip the screen, close a window, quitting requesters, starting
programs and actions just by pressing buttons on your remote. No visible GUI,
dock or something like that. Just you in front of your screen. I am using
IRComRemote a few years for presentations and it's quite useful.@{par}

@endnode
@node "Systemrequirements" "Systemrequirements"

@{MS "System requirements"}

IRComRemote (should work) works on all Amigas with OS 2.0 or higher.
Some features require OS3.0 or up!@{par}

This application requires the IRCom driver system which is the interface to
external infrared hardware and infrared signals.@{par}

@endnode
@node "Featurelist" "Features"

@{MS "Features"}

° Commodity@{par}

° Easy configuration@{par}

° Online Help@{par}

° Locale Support@{par}

@endnode
